<HEADLINE>
FT  08 APR 93 / World News in Brief: Scudamore retires from racing
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Peter Scudamore, eight times national hunt champion jockey, has retired from
racing only four days after the Grand National fiasco.
</TEXT>
<XX>
