FT  06 APR 93 / UK Company News: Dolphin dives to Pounds 1.5m
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
DOLPHIN Packaging con-tinued to suffer from difficult trading conditions in
1992 and saw pre-tax profit halved, from Pounds 3.03m to Pounds 1.51m.
The dividend, however, is maintained at 4.5p with a final of 2.8p. Earnings
per share were 5.22p (10.55p).
