chairman.
Dolphin and DRG Plastics have agreed to settle their dispute which began in
June 1991, after DRG brought legal proceedings against Dolphin regarding its
rotary thermoforming process.
The agreement maintains the confidentiality of the process with Dolphin
selling its rotary thermoforming machinery to DRG at an agreed commercial
value.
